B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Race</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Dynasty</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Justman\" title=\"House Justman\">House Justman</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Benedict_I_Justman\" title=\"Benedict I Justman\">Benedict I Justman</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Benedict II Justman</b> was the second <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Trident\" title=\"King of the Trident\">King of the Trident</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Justman\" title=\"House Justman\">House Justman</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Benedict_II_Justman&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Benedict II was the son and heir of the founder of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Justman\" title=\"House Justman\">House Justman</a>, King <a href=\"/index.php/Benedict_I_Justman\" title=\"Benedict I Justman\">Benedict I</a>. Benedict II ruled for sixty years, adding <a href=\"/index.php/Duskendale\" title=\"Duskendale\">Duskendale</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Rosby\" title=\"Rosby\">Rosby</a>, and the mouth of the <a href=\"/index.php/Blackwater_Rush\" title=\"Blackwater Rush\">Blackwater Rush</a> to the Justman realm.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Benedict_II_Justman&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackwood\" title=\"House Blackwood\">Blackwood</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px dashed black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_Bracken\" title=\"House Bracken\">Bracken</a></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div><